      • generateDeleteMetadataSql

        protected String generateDeleteMetadataSql(CreateSpatialIndexStatement statement,
                               liquibase.database.Database database)
        Generates the SQL for deleting any existing record from the USER_SDO_GEOM_METADATA table. Typically this record shouldn't be present but we must ensure that it does not already exist.
        Parameters:
        statement - the create spatial index statement.
        database - the database instance.
        Returns:
        the SQL to delete any existing metadata record.

      • generateInsertMetadataSql

        protected String generateInsertMetadataSql(CreateSpatialIndexStatement statement,
                               liquibase.database.Database database)
        Generates the SQL for inserting the necessary record into the USER_SDO_GEOM_METADATA table. This record must be present prior to creating the spatial index.
        Parameters:
        statement - the create spatial index statement.
        database - the database instance.
        Returns:
        the SQL to insert the metadata record.
